    "title": {
      "rendered": "How Nonprofits Can Increase Reach and Engagement Using Facebook Notes"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/How-Nonprofits-Can-Increase-Facebook-Reach-and-Engagement-Using-Notes-Square.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19347\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-19347\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/How-Nonprofits-Can-Increase-Facebook-Reach-and-Engagement-Using-Notes-Square-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"How Nonprofits Can Increase Facebook Reach and Engagement Using Notes Square\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/How-Nonprofits-Can-Increase-Facebook-Reach-and-Engagement-Using-Notes-Square.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/How-Nonprofits-Can-Increase-Facebook-Reach-and-Engagement-Using-Notes-Square.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/How-Nonprofits-Can-Increase-Facebook-Reach-and-Engagement-Using-Notes-Square.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/How-Nonprofits-Can-Increase-Facebook-Reach-and-Engagement-Using-Notes-Square.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/How-Nonprofits-Can-Increase-Facebook-Reach-and-Engagement-Using-Notes-Square.jpg?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Facebook Notes is a native app that was popular when Facebook Pages first launched in 2007, but as Status Updates and the News Feed took\u00a0precedence, the Facebook Notes app\u00a0quickly lost prominence. Most nonprofits have likely removed the Notes app in the years since, but you may be surprised to find it \u2013 and many other apps that you quit using years ago \u2013 still &#8220;Added&#8221; to your page.</p>\n<p>In September 2015 as <strong><a href=\"https://medium.com/@nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\">Medium</a></strong> began to increase in popularity, <strong><a href=\"http://newsroom.fb.com/news/2015/09/updates-for-facebook-notes/\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook resurrected the Notes app with a new design</a></strong> and still today Notes <em>seem</em> to get more exposure in the News Feed (though for how long, nobody knows). If you are like most nonprofits on Facebook and\u00a0have experienced\u00a0dramatic loss in reach and engagement over the last year, then experimenting with publishing Notes on Facebook to increase reach and engagement as an alternative to spending on adverting is worth a shot. On the Nonprofit Tech for Good Facebook Page Notes are currently receiving 3X the reach and engagement as photos and links. That said, here&#8217;s how to get started with Facebook Notes.</p>\n<h1>1. Go to Settings &gt; Apps &gt; Add Notes App (if it is not already added).</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19320\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19320\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Add-the-Facebook-Notes-App.png?resize=600%2C274\" alt=\"Add the Facebook Notes App\" width=\"600\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Add-the-Facebook-Notes-App.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Add-the-Facebook-Notes-App.png?resize=300%2C137&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">2. Go to Timeline &gt; Offer, Event+ &gt; Note.</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19322\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19322\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Post-Note-from-Facebook.png?resize=600%2C273\" alt=\"Post Note from Facebook\" width=\"600\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Post-Note-from-Facebook.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Post-Note-from-Facebook.png?resize=300%2C137&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>3. Upload a cover photo (1200 X 445) and write a title.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19324\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19324\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Upload-Photo-Header.png?resize=600%2C280\" alt=\"Upload Photo Header\" width=\"600\" height=\"280\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Upload-Photo-Header.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Upload-Photo-Header.png?resize=300%2C140&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>4. Upload your nonprofit&#8217;s logo, add content, insert links, and format content.</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19325\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19325\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Add-content.png?resize=600%2C294\" alt=\"Add content\" width=\"600\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Add-content.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Add-content.png?resize=300%2C147&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>5. Save or Publish.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Save.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19327\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19327\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Save.png?resize=600%2C285\" alt=\"Save\" width=\"600\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Save.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Save.png?resize=300%2C143&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>6. Once published, <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/nonprofit-tech-for-good/36-useful-apps-online-tools-for-nonprofits/10154174336728273\" target=\"_blank\">review</a>.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/nonprofit-tech-for-good/36-useful-apps-online-tools-for-nonprofits/10154174336728273\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19333\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19333\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/REVIEW-2.png?resize=425%2C595\" alt=\"REVIEW\" width=\"425\" height=\"595\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/REVIEW-2.png?w=425&amp;ssl=1 425w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/REVIEW-2.png?resize=214%2C300&amp;ssl=1 214w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>7. Edit, if necessary.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/nonprofit-tech-for-good/36-useful-apps-online-tools-for-nonprofits/10154174336728273\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19334\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19334\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/EDIT.png?resize=600%2C295\" alt=\"EDIT\" width=\"600\" height=\"295\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/EDIT.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/EDIT.png?resize=300%2C148&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1>8. Monitor Insights for Notes to see how they compare to other posts.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19335\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19335\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/INSIGHTS.png?resize=600%2C285\" alt=\"INSIGHTS\" width=\"600\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/INSIGHTS.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/INSIGHTS.png?resize=300%2C143&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\">9. Go to Timelime &gt; Manage Tabs &gt; Drag and Drop &gt; Save &gt; Review.</h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19338\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19338\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-1-1.png?resize=600%2C238\" alt=\"Manage Tab 1\" width=\"600\" height=\"238\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-1-1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-1-1.png?resize=300%2C119&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19339\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19339\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-2.png?resize=600%2C393\" alt=\"Manage Tab 2\" width=\"600\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-2.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nonprofitorgs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-19340\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19340\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-3.png?resize=600%2C238\" alt=\"Manage Tab 3\" width=\"600\" height=\"238\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-3.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Manage-Tab-3.png?resize=300%2C119&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
